Two Weeks Later [id=fba3_followup_section]
----------------
psych_sba_sidebar6 -> fba3_progress_graph_2

JJ: That looks much better!

Annie: I know, right? My roommate is much happier. He is going to bed on time more often, and his parents even asked my roommate for her secrets on how she got him to go to bed on time!

Lin: That's amazing! I'm so glad we were able to help this time.

